---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="main-content">
        <section class="hero page-section" id="inicio">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="hero-content" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <h1><span class="lang lang-pt">Trading Automatizado com <span class="highlight">Rigor Científico</span>.</span><span class="lang lang-es">Trading Automatizado con <span class="highlight">Rigor Científico</span>.</span><span class="lang lang-en">Automated Trading with <span class="highlight">Scientific Rigor</span>.</span></h1>
                    <p><span class="lang lang-pt">Desenvolvo Expert Advisors para MQL5 que unem análise quantitativa e tecnologia para otimizar seus resultados no mercado financeiro.</span><span class="lang lang-es">Desarrollo Expert Advisors para MQL5 que combinan análisis cuantitativo y tecnología para optimizar sus resultados en el mercado financiero.</span><span class="lang lang-en">I develop MQL5 Expert Advisors that merge quantitative analysis and technology to optimize your results in the financial market.</span></p>
                    <a href="#produtos" class="button"><span class="lang lang-pt">Conheça os Produtos</span><span class="lang lang-es">Conoce los Productos</span><span class="lang lang-en">Explore Products</span></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="blog" class="page-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title" data-aos="fade-up"><span class="lang lang-pt">Blog & Pesquisas</span><span class="lang lang-es">Blog & Investigación</span><span class="lang lang-en">Blog & Research</span></h2>
                <div class="blog-tabs" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <button class="tab-button active" data-tab="geral"><span class="lang lang-pt">Conceitos Gerais</span></button>
                    <button class="tab-button" data-tab="intermediario"><span class="lang lang-pt">Conceitos Intermediários</span></button>
                </div>
                <div id="tab-geral" class="tab-content active">
                    <div class="grid-layout">
                        <div class="card blog-card" data-aos="fade-up">
                            <h3><span class="lang lang-pt">Aplicações de IA no Mercado</span></h3>
                            <p class="card-content"><span class="lang lang-pt">Como a IA está transformando o trading e a gestão de risco.</span></p>
                            <a href="#" class="button"><span class="lang lang-pt">Leia o Artigo</span></a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card blog-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                            <h3><span class="lang lang-pt">A Arte do Backtesting Robusto</span></h3>
                            <p class="card-content"><span class="lang lang-pt">Evite o sobreajuste (overfitting) e valide suas estratégias da forma correta.</span></p>
                            <a href="#" class="button"><span class="lang lang-pt">Leia Mais</span></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="produtos" class="page-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title" data-aos="fade-up">Expert Advisors</h2>
                <div class="grid-layout">
                    <div class="card product-card" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/Ssp9H0Dv/nexus-ea-forex-mt5-logo-200x200-6618.png" alt="Logo Nexus EA">
                        <h3>Nexus EA Forex MT5</h3>
                        <p class="card-content"><span class="lang lang-pt">Sistema diversificado e robusto, operando com 9 estratégias em até 8 pares de moedas.</span></p>
                        <a href="#" class="button"><span class="lang lang-pt">Saber Mais</span></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card product-card" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/PJJ5R2s7/axis-neural-ea-for-mt5-logo-200x200-6888.png" alt="Logo AXIS Neural EA">
                        <h3>AXIS Neural EA</h3>
                        <p class="card-content"><span class="lang lang-pt">A vanguarda do trading neural. Uma ferramenta de alta performance que utiliza IA para se adaptar ao mercado.</span></p>
                        <a href="#" class="button"><span class="lang lang-pt">Saber Mais</span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section id="sobre" class="page-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="card" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; text-align: left;">
                        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/mgspR5D0/C-pia-de-Beige-Minimalist-Initial-Brand-Logo-Instagram-Post-1.png" alt="Foto de Enrique Enguix" style="width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%;">
                        <div style="flex: 1;">
                            <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: left; margin: 0 0 1rem 0;">Enrique Enguix</h2>
                            <p style="font-size: 1.1em;"><span class="lang lang-pt">Olá! Sou um Analista Quantitativo e Desenvolvedor MQL5. Minha paixão é criar uma ponte entre a teoria acadêmica e a prática do trading, oferecendo soluções robustas e conteúdo de qualidade para traders em todo o mundo.</span></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contato" class="page-section">
            <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
                <h2 class="section-title" data-aos="fade-up"><span class="lang lang-pt">Entre em Contato</span></h2>
                <div class="contact-options" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <button class="tab-button active" data-contact="form"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i><span class="lang lang-pt"> Dúvidas & Suporte</span></button>
                </div>
                <div id="contact-form" class="contact-details active">
                    <div class="card">
                        <form name="contato" data-netlify="true">
                            <div class="form-group"><label for="name"><span class="lang lang-pt">Nome</span></label><input type="text" id="name" name="name" required></div>
                            <div class="form-group"><label for="email">Email</label><input type="email" id="email" name="email" required></div>
                            <div class="form-group"><label for="message"><span class="lang lang-pt">Mensagem</span></label><textarea id="message" name="message" required rows="5"></textarea></div>
                            <button type="submit" class="button"><span class="lang lang-pt">Enviar Mensagem</span></button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>
